> > > LU sent key1: FD 14 D4 74 2A
> > > Drive Authentic - using varient 0
> > > LU sent challenge: 23 22 8E F5 86 EE BB 8B CB 3F
> > > Host sending key 2: 8D 8D 6B C7 9B
> > > DVD is authenticated
> > > Received Session Key:   B6 3D 2A 82 94
> > > not Authenticated
